    <title>MELODY</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container-fluid"> 
    <div id="quizContainer70" class="">

<!-- WELCOME -->
<h1 class="display-6 mb-5 bellota text-center" style="background-image: url('../images/scoresby/melody.gif');background-size: contain;"><span class="px-2 white-text" style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.871); line-height: 1.5;">Five characteristics of a</span><br><span class="px-2 white-text" style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.871); line-height: 1.5;">great melody</span></h1>

<p class="text-center grey-text my-5">Virtual keyboard provided for you to play with: <a href="https://www.onlinepianist.com/virtual-piano" target="_blank">Virtual keyboard</a></p>

<form style="line-height: 2.5;" class="text-center mb-5" action="/sendMelodyToHanford" method="POST">

  <div class="quizQuestionContainer"><p class="white-text my-5"><span style="font-size: 2.5rem;"><span class="green-text">Characteristic 1</span></span><br>Most good melodies restrict their basic range to no more than an octave-and-a-half.</p>
    <div class="responsive-container mb-5" style="height:350px;"></div>
    <p class="text-center white-text">Australian music example: Dance Monkey - Tones and I</p>
    <div class="responsive-container mb-2"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/q0hyYWKXF0Q?start=23" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>
    <textarea class="d-block w-100 mb-3 text-center" placeholder="In your own words, reflect on...
    1. What this characteristic means
    2. Why it is a good characteristic to have" name="RangeReflection" id="RangeReflection" rows="8" required></textarea>
  </div>

  <div class="quizQuestionContainer2"><p class="white-text my-5"><span style="font-size: 2.5rem;"><span class="green-text">Characteristic 2</span></span><br>Most good melodies use repeating elements.</p>
    <div class="responsive-container mb-5" style="height:350px;"></div>
    <p class="text-center white-text">Australian music example: Little Things - Ziggy Ramo ft. Paul Kelly</p>
    <div class="responsive-container mb-2"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/pk6dgf0EnmU?start=101" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>
    <textarea class="d-block w-100 mb-3 text-center" placeholder="In your own words, reflect on...
    1. What this characteristic means
    2. Why it is a good characteristic to have" name="RepeatReflection" id="RepeatReflection" rows="8" required></textarea>
  </div>

  <div class="quizQuestionContainer"><p class="white-text my-5"><span style="font-size: 2.5rem;"><span class="green-text">Characteristic 3</span></span><br>Most good melodies are comprised of stepwise motion (i.e., move by scale steps), with occasional leaps.</p>
    <div class="responsive-container mb-5" style="height:350px;"></div>
    <p class="text-center white-text mb-2">Australian music example:<a target="_blank" href="https://youtu.be/Nt0NcaxmGHo?t=18"> Don't be Rama Rama - Warburton Community</a></p>
    <textarea class="d-block w-100 mb-3 text-center" placeholder="In your own words, reflect on...
    1. What this characteristic means
    2. Why it is a good characteristic to have" name="MotionReflection" id="MotionReflection" rows="8" required></textarea>
  </div>

  <div class="quizQuestionContainer2"><p class="white-text my-5"><span style="font-size: 2.5rem;"><span class="green-text">Characteristic 4</span></span><br>Most good melodies have a discernible relationship with the bass line.</p>
    <div class="responsive-container mb-5" style="height:350px;"></div>
    <p class="text-center white-text">Australian music example: Prejudice - Tim Minchen</p>
    <div class="responsive-container mb-2"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KVN_0qvuhhw?start=344" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>
    <textarea class="d-block w-100 mb-3 text-center" placeholder="In your own words, reflect on...
    1. What this characteristic means
    2. Why it is a good characteristic to have" name="BasslineReflection" id="BasslineReflection" rows="8" required></textarea>
  </div>

  <div class="quizQuestionContainer"><p class="white-text my-5"><span style="font-size: 2.5rem;"><span class="green-text">Characteristic 5</span></span><br>Most good melodies have a climactic point.</p>
    <div class="responsive-container mb-5" style="height:350px;"></div>
    <p class="text-center white-text">Australian music example: Choral Symphony - Carl Vine</p>
    <div class="responsive-container mb-2"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ryX2xEjf3wQ?start=1670" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>
    <textarea class="d-block w-100 mb-3 text-center" placeholder="In your own words, reflect on...
    1. What this characteristic means
    2. Why it is a good characteristic to have" name="ClimaxReflection" id="ClimaxReflection" rows="8" required></textarea>
  </div>

  <div class="quizQuestionContainer text-center">
    <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= csrfToken %>">
    <input class="mx-3 my-3 text-center" type="text" name="Student" placeholder="Your name" required></input>
    <input class="mx-3 my-3" type="submit"></input>
  </div>
</form>

